value.soql: SELECT Id, EpicorCustId__c, EpicorCustNum__c, Name, AccountSource, BillingCity, BillingCountry, BillingPostalCode, BillingState, BillingStreet, CreatedById, CreatedDate, Description, Industry, ParentId, ParentAccount__c, ShippingCity, ShippingCountry, ShippingPostalCode, ShippingState, ShippingStreet, Type, Phone, Fax, AccountNumber FROM Account

properties.name: where-clause
properties.value: WHERE EpicorCustId__c LIKE 'ECSF%'  and EpicorCustNum__c = null
